    },
    {
      "start": 35.03,
      "end": 36.81,
      "text": "8월에 함께하는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.81,
      "end": 39.73,
      "text": "A Computer Animated Horror Comedy"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.73,
      "end": 41.83,
      "text": "Monster Family"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.83,
      "end": 43.25,
      "text": "Welcome, Chris."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.51,
      "end": 44.33,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.33,
      "end": 46.07,
      "text": "What's up with you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.45,
      "end": 47.05,
      "text": "Good morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 48.51,
      "end": 50.91,
      "text": "오늘 메시지가 하나가 왔는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.91,
      "end": 51.91,
      "text": "이거 한번 들어보실래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.99,
      "end": 52.25,
      "text": "OK"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.25,
      "end": 54.85,
      "text": "0653님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.85,
      "end": 56.37,
      "text": "Chris, 반가워요."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.87,
      "end": 59.11,
      "text": "아이들 사진 봤는데 정말 귀여워요."
    },
    {
      "start": 59.33,
      "end": 60.27,
      "text": "이렇게 보내주셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.59,
      "end": 61.53,
      "text": "Oh, thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.65,
      "end": 62.05,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.25,
      "end": 64.39,
      "text": "I brought them to the studio the other day."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.49,
      "end": 64.91,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.07,
      "end": 66.13,
      "text": "My whole family."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.29,
      "end": 66.71,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 67.25,
      "end": 70.11,
      "text": "Already we uploaded the photo of your family."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.39,
      "end": 70.73,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.73,
      "end": 71.05,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.05,
      "end": 71.11,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.31,
      "end": 75.37,
      "text": "우리 SNS 채널에도 우리가 업로드를 시켜드렸는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.37,
      "end": 77.21,
      "text": "그거 확인하신 분들이 꽤 많이 계시더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.63,
      "end": 82.21,
      "text": "They met many good emo's and a Sam-chon here at GMP."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.45,
      "end": 83.01,
      "text": "Am I emo?"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.27,
      "end": 83.89,
      "text": "You're an emo."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.89,
      "end": 85.83,
      "text": "There's a couple more emo's."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.91,
      "end": 86.19,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.39,
      "end": 87.25,
      "text": "And Sam-chon도 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.25,
      "end": 89.59,
      "text": "자카 이모스 and PD님 Sam-chon."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.89,
      "end": 90.09,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.41,
      "end": 92.17,
      "text": "너무 즐거운 시간이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.19,
      "end": 93.39,
      "text": "덕분에 즐거웠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.51,
      "end": 93.73,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.37,
      "end": 97.21,
      "text": "우리가 이제 영화의 내용으로 좀 들어가서요."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.43,
      "end": 101.81,
      "text": "All the characters in these animations are so charming."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.39,
      "end": 104.49,
      "text": "They all have their unique character."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.69,
      "end": 104.95,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.09,
      "end": 105.69,
      "text": "So adorable."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.27,
      "end": 106.45,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.93,
      "end": 107.95,
      "text": "But among them,"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.05,
      "end": 108.81,
      "text": "그들 중에서요,"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.89,
      "end": 111.27,
      "text": "there's one character with a unique way of speaking."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.47,
      "end": 114.25,
      "text": "Ah, remember that unique, very unique character."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.25,
      "end": 124.67,
      "text": "Ah, you know, do?"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.05,
      "end": 126.55,
      "text": "You know, yo-da?"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.63,
      "end": 128.83,
      "text": "Yo-da 아시는 분 많이 계신지 모르겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.09,
      "end": 129.71,
      "text": "Do you like yo-da?"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.09,
      "end": 130.57,
      "text": "I don't."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.67,
      "end": 133.79,
      "text": "I never really liked him because he's just a little."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.89,
      "end": 134.57,
      "text": "Oh, you too."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.31,
      "end": 137.11,
      "text": "I mean, there's not much to like."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.59,
      "end": 138.73,
      "text": "He's like a little."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.95,
      "end": 141.21,
      "text": "He reminded me of a cockroach."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.33,
      "end": 141.85,
      "text": "Not a cockroach."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.03,
      "end": 142.37,
      "text": "Sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.59,
      "end": 143.45,
      "text": "I mean a rat."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.45,
      "end": 143.77,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.03,
      "end": 144.79,
      "text": "A big rat."
    },
    {
      "start": 145.88,
      "end": 147.44,
      "text": "A toad."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.5,
      "end": 148.12,
      "text": "A big toad."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.18,
      "end": 148.68,
      "text": "That was it."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.78,
      "end": 149.28,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.3,
      "end": 149.7,
      "text": "A toad."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.82,
      "end": 150.36,
      "text": "Yeah, okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.36,
      "end": 150.52,
      "text": "A gobby."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.72,
      "end": 151.42,
      "text": "Okay, okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 151.52,
      "end": 152.78,
      "text": "Oh, 좀 비슷하게 생긴 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 152.9,
      "end": 154.38,
      "text": "But as I get older and wiser,"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.56,
      "end": 156.66,
      "text": "I can see he's a very wise,"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.22,
      "end": 159.14,
      "text": "very genius kind of man."
    },
    {
      "start": 159.3,
      "end": 159.52,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.18,
      "end": 172.44,
      "text": "Oh, it's a classic."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.56,
      "end": 173.16,
      "text": "All-time classic."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.16,
      "end": 173.6,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.02,
      "end": 175.28,
      "text": "So the witch in this movie,"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.6,
      "end": 176.38,
      "text": "Baba Yaga,"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.58,
      "end": 176.92,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.28,
      "end": 179.22,
      "text": "She speaks very mysteriously."
    },
    {
      "start": 179.46,
      "end": 180.92,
      "text": "If you listen carefully,"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.08,
      "end": 183.04,
      "text": "you can understand everything she says."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.14,
      "end": 184.02,
      "text": "Yeah, amazing."
    },
    {
      "start": 184.2,
      "end": 185.0,
      "text": "Just the grammar"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.0,
      "end": 186.64,
      "text": "is very different"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.64,
      "end": 188.96,
      "text": "than your typical spoken grammar."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.18,
      "end": 189.52,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.74,
      "end": 190.1,
      "text": "But yeah,"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.16,
      "end": 193.3,
      "text": "her way of speaking is based off yo-da."
    },
    {
      "start": 193.46,
      "end": 194.8,
      "text": "The wise yo-da."
    },
    {
      "start": 194.8,
      "end": 195.3,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 195.3,
      "end": 198.3,
      "text": "이 바바야가라는 캐릭터가 있었잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.68,
      "end": 200.34,
      "text": "말투가 정말 재밌지 않습니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.08,
      "end": 202.52,
      "text": "근데 이 바바야가는"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.52,
      "end": 205.86,
      "text": "슬라브 신화 속의 마녀에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.86,
      "end": 206.76,
      "text": "영감을 받아서"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.76,
      "end": 207.86,
      "text": "이렇게 모티브를 삼아서"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.86,
      "end": 210.24,
      "text": "만든 캐릭터라고 생각하시면 되고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.24,
      "end": 211.2,
      "text": "From a witch?"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.42,
      "end": 213.4,
      "text": "From Slavic mythology?"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.6,
      "end": 213.78,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.78,
      "end": 214.32,
      "text": "Sort of"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.32,
      "end": 216.6,
      "text": "Russia 마녀라고 생각할 수도 있겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.66,
      "end": 217.0,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.36,
      "end": 218.0,
      "text": "Interesting."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.0,
      "end": 218.52,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.7,
      "end": 220.32,
      "text": "목소리 연기를 한 배우가"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.32,
      "end": 220.94,
      "text": "또 아주"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.94,
      "end": 223.82,
      "text": "배우가 아주 연기를 잘했는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.28,
      "end": 226.4,
      "text": "Catherine Tate라는 사람이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 226.52,
      "end": 226.72,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 226.8,
      "end": 228.72,
      "text": "She's an English actress and comedian."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.38,
      "end": 231.22,
      "text": "I saw some of her comedy skits."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.72,
      "end": 232.7,
      "text": "They were pretty funny."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.78,
      "end": 234.8,
      "text": "And you can tell that"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.8,
      "end": 235.54,
      "text": "Baba Yaga"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.54,
      "end": 237.92,
      "text": "you have to be a funny character"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.92,
      "end": 239.46,
      "text": "to play the voice"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.46,
      "end": 240.5,
      "text": "of this witch."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.5,
      "end": 242.3,
      "text": "그래서 연기가"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.3,
      "end": 244.16,
      "text": "결국에 그 사람의 성품을"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.16,
      "end": 245.3,
      "text": "다 반영을 하다 보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.3,
      "end": 247.44,
      "text": "그렇게 바바야가의 캐릭터를"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.44,
      "end": 249.18,
      "text": "잘 소화하지 않았나 싶습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.86,
      "end": 250.5,
      "text": "아, okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.7,
      "end": 251.08,
      "text": "자, 그러면"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.08,
      "end": 252.64,
      "text": "오늘 장면에서 왠지"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.64,
      "end": 254.12,
      "text": "이 바바야가의 목소리를"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.12,
      "end": 255.54,
      "text": "좀 더 들을 수 있을 것 같죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.68,
      "end": 256.12,
      "text": "Can't wait."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.14,
      "end": 257.06,
      "text": "네, 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.2,
      "end": 259.4,
      "text": "I hate that my daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.4,
      "end": 260.9,
      "text": "does nothing but insult me"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.9,
      "end": 263.08,
      "text": "and I hate that my kids"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.08,
      "end": 263.98,
      "text": "are always fighting"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.98,
      "end": 265.64,
      "text": "and I hate that my husband"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.64,
      "end": 267.66,
      "text": "just sleeps through it all."
    },
    {
      "start": 267.66,
      "end": 269.22,
      "text": "Work it will"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.22,
      "end": 271.54,
      "text": "my transformation spell"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.54,
      "end": 273.14,
      "text": "So very unhappy"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.14,
      "end": 274.18,
      "text": "you are"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.18,
      "end": 276.06,
      "text": "Perceptive you are"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.06,
      "end": 278.02,
      "text": "Help, Baba Yaga"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.02,
      "end": 278.48,
      "text": "win"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.48,
      "end": 279.92,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.12,
      "end": 280.42,
      "text": "How?"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.8,
      "end": 281.9,
      "text": "By car singing"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.9,
      "end": 284.73,
      "text": "Oh, Emma's family"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.73,
      "end": 285.45,
      "text": "thought it was"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.45,
      "end": 286.21,
      "text": "a Halloween party"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.21,
      "end": 286.83,
      "text": "but sadly"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.83,
      "end": 287.73,
      "text": "it wasn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.73,
      "end": 288.23,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.41,
      "end": 288.75,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.75,
      "end": 290.13,
      "text": "She was trying to go"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.13,
      "end": 291.59,
      "text": "to a Halloween party"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.59,
      "end": 293.05,
      "text": "but she ended up"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.05,
      "end": 293.71,
      "text": "going to"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.71,
      "end": 294.63,
      "text": "a concert"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.63,
      "end": 296.43,
      "text": "It was a rock concert"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.43,
      "end": 297.41,
      "text": "and"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.41,
      "end": 298.21,
      "text": "the people"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.21,
      "end": 298.93,
      "text": "the security"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.93,
      "end": 299.77,
      "text": "there"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.77,
      "end": 300.47,
      "text": "thought"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.47,
      "end": 301.29,
      "text": "her family"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.29,
      "end": 302.23,
      "text": "was the band"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.23,
      "end": 303.25,
      "text": "the music"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.25,
      "end": 304.67,
      "text": "얼마나 당황스러웠을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.75,
      "end": 306.09,
      "text": "진짜 당황했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.09,
      "end": 306.59,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.59,
      "end": 308.21,
      "text": "그리고 그 가족끼리"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.21,
      "end": 309.59,
      "text": "they just blamed each other"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.59,
      "end": 309.93,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.93,
      "end": 310.39,
      "text": "Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.39,
      "end": 311.21,
      "text": "막 탓하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.21,
      "end": 312.55,
      "text": "이러는 장면이 보였어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.55,
      "end": 313.35,
      "text": "Especially mom"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.35,
      "end": 315.03,
      "text": "It's all your fault, mom"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.03,
      "end": 317.07,
